markdownRemark.html:
After taking the course Practical Deep Learning For Coders 2019, I developed a model that can classify between all 600 SNES games by screenshot. Upload a screenshot of any game at any point; the model will tell you which game it belongs to.

  • Online Demo
  • Code and explanations

frontmatter.title: Visually Classifying between 600 SNES games with 94% accuracy
